public class FillLocaleTask
extends org.apache.tools.ant.Task

Fills missing keys in locale with the values found in a different locale in teh same file. <fillLocale localeXML="filled/filled-main-default-FR.xml" targetXML="complete/main-default.xml" sourceLocale="en_US" targetLocale="it_IT" doSetReviewFlag="false" fillOnlyKeysStartingWith="key_line" />
